This is not company culture.
This is a startup loyalty ritual.

In today’s episode of “Silicon Valley Has Lost Its Mind,” we’re looking at an AI startup that thought the best way to prove culture was having employees show up with matching lip tattoos for a product launch. Not equity. Not stability. Just vibes, venture capital, and a camera pointed at LinkedIn.
